downloadTitle: .NET Rocks! - Dot Net Nuke Discussion Panel
downloadDescription: Carl and Richard interview members of the Dot Net Nuke corporation and their partners in front of a live audience at the Connections conference in Las Vegas November, 2007.
detailsSection: The .NET Nuke Panel consists of Scott Willhite, Shaun Walker, Joe Brinkman, Nik Kalyani, amd Larry Augustin.
systemRequirementsSection: Presentations are played using the Microsoft Windows Media Player.
installInstructionSection:
- Select "Save this Program to Disk" to copy the download to your machine for installation at a later time.
- Once the file has been downloaded, execute it in order to extract the media file.
